{"tid":344531,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]部新機裝完os mon speaker冇聲","createTime":"2017-08-02T10:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T12:23:25.000Z","uid":75737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ed91acb0a9b84519651fe51561b732ad748fa6fb","tid":344531,"uid":75737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T10:44:25.000Z","msg":"用隻新ssd裝win10 ，搞掂哂啲driver之後開下歌黎聽點知mon個speaker冇聲出，耳機插前板都冇聲 <br />\n<br />\n跟住按右下角個喇叭icon由realtek hd audio轉用sharkoon機箱個7.1 extension, mon有聲出但好細聲，前板插headset出聲正常<br />\n<br />\n我以前hdd都係win 10，用過佢黎開機播歌都冇問題，realtek同7.1都正常運作。<br />\n啱啱重裝win10個realtek都係用唔到冇聲 到底邊到出問題? <br />\n<br />\ngoogle過話win10會自己default用耳機口出聲，但我已經設定左mon喇叭係預設裝置"},{"pid":"2c6c0bfdaf1a9d905b4fd09317b8aa1c2eda1ad1","tid":344531,"uid":75737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T11:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd0e08d3e8f87326ebaeadc9a0423c8d2bb0c6a","tid":344531,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T11:17:40.000Z","msg":"停用另一個"},{"pid":"7813ef44196603099231de4ddcde3281fbab5287","tid":344531,"uid":75737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T11:23:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>停用另一個</blockquote><br />\n停左 都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"438d5e3a2e41502a0afb2d8ced0e673b63e60e83","tid":344531,"uid":75737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T11:27:38.000Z","msg":"佢播歌個時綠色volume個到都識跳下跳下好正常，咁係咪底板問題<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/02/192723_9e689ff0db87ed57ee3b2316d43f6920.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F02%2F192723_9e689ff0db87ed57ee3b2316d43f6920.PNG&h=010381cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e05e733b52a7e0a94063e067dc3f313b81df688f","tid":344531,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T